headline: Inflation clouds Fed’s path, White House eyes Intel stake
summary: July’s consumer price index held steady at 2.7% year-over-year — slightly below expectations — offering a brief sense of relief.

headline: Investing.com’s stocks of the week
summary: Investing.com -- It has been a very positive week for U.S. equities as earnings season winds down, with the S&P 500 hitting a new high. While Friday saw traders take some gains off the table, stocks appear poised to close the week higher.
